'''Dr. Barrett''' is an [[attending]] in the [[Seattle Grace Mercy West Hospital]] [[Emergency Room]].

==History==
When [[Adele Webber]] was vomiting up blood in the ER, Barrett is the doctor who called [[Richard Webber]] to inform him. He treated Adele in the ER until her care was taken over by [[Miranda Bailey]].

==Career==
He is a doctor in the [[Emergency Room]] of [[Seattle Grace Mercy West Hospital]].
